    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AROHEL: CALL OF THE WIND</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arohel</strong> is set in a near future, when a series of mass flooding across the entire Earth has forced survivors to take refuge on stilt complexes. A few years later, a meteor shower reached the Earth, bringing with it a mysterious crystal of unknown origin: the Arohel. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By connecting with the Arohel, fragments of land began to emerge from the waters, clumping together and forming floating islands that, after a cycle of about 12 hours, disappeared back into the abyss, only to reappear the next day in different arrangements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the settlements, a new group of intrepid adventurer arose, tasked with finding new resources for the community: the Explorers. In &quot;Arohel: Call Of The Wind,&quot; you will play as a novice Explorer, navigating through procedurally generated floating islands on a quest to find a long-lost friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077720/extras/d0aceddfa0286a6ef86a62c199baa41b.poster.avif?t=1772381552\" width=500 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077720/extras/d0aceddfa0286a6ef86a62c199baa41b.webm?t=1772381552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077720/extras/d0aceddfa0286a6ef86a62c199baa41b.mp4?t=1772381552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive through the floating islands and explore them with your grappling hook and hang glider. Take on procedurally generated missions from your fellow villagers, collecting important resources to help your community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LOOT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077720/extras/81c56a704e5cb9163cdea9fd7e20f514.poster.avif?t=1772381552\" width=500 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077720/extras/81c56a704e5cb9163cdea9fd7e20f514.webm?t=1772381552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077720/extras/81c56a704e5cb9163cdea9fd7e20f514.mp4?t=1772381552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The archipelagoes are procedurally generated, therefore, every journey to the floating islands offers a unique and unpredictable experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIGHT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077720/extras/a72da5c1d865465c554740279025f112.poster.avif?t=1772381552\" width=500 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077720/extras/a72da5c1d865465c554740279025f112.webm?t=1772381552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077720/extras/a72da5c1d865465c554740279025f112.mp4?t=1772381552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a diverse array of enemies and engage in thrilling and epic boss fights. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TRADE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077720/extras/0fdb412b849285683e93b5335445d25f.poster.avif?t=1772381552\" width=500 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077720/extras/0fdb412b849285683e93b5335445d25f.webm?t=1772381552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077720/extras/0fdb412b849285683e93b5335445d25f.mp4?t=1772381552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trade resources for Seeds, the in-game currency, to purchase new equipment, upgrade your tools, and most importantly, enhance your flying car to explore increasingly distant archipelagoes and progress through the story.</p>",
